{"tid":278158,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"6 月 22 日局你用！八達通 App 將與「好易畀」O! ePay 應用合拼！","createTime":"2017-06-10T08:20:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T02:04:00.000Z","uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7925907eec5bf77c5b326bb10bb9a5fa395383f","tid":278158,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T08:20:35.000Z","msg":"八達通公司是市面上的電子支付龍頭，可是發展電子錢包的發展不太理想，推出一段時間的「好易畀」O! ePay 普及度也不太高。今天，官方公佈將會在 6 月 22 日推出新應用程式，正式把八達通 App 將與「好易畀」O! ePay 應用程式合拼。<br />\n<br />\n由 2017 年 6 月 22 日起， O! ePay App將會與八達通App合併，用戶可以於一個手機 App 內，同時處理八達通及O! ePay 賬戶，並享有更多功能。<br />\n<br />\n用戶只需下載於 2017 年 6 月 22 日推出的全新八達通 App，如已下載八達通 App，請於當日更新程式至最新版本，然後用戶可以現時的密碼登入O! ePay 賬戶，便可繼續使用O! ePay、查閱八達通餘額及網上付款等服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hksilicon.com/articles/1353735\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hksilicon.com%2Farticles%2F1353735&d=vCgATC7UJM1bjoNEo%2FwUYDM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=828f5735\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hksilicon.com/articles/1353735</a><br />\n<br />\n個app我淨係用黎做太陽能電筒<br />\n幫屋企人八達通增值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5820e624f2720e84ca415a0af1c037e75803106d","tid":278158,"uid":10906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-10T10:49:43.000Z","msg":"即係用查餘額就迫鳩人用埋個乜柒 pay？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f36e7653d93a3af6a1e78640c81c346cb46e4868","tid":278158,"uid":66055,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-26T05:31:15.000Z","msg":"有新野又點 香港廢中廢老都係唔會用<br />\n<br />\n佢地眼中只有微信錢包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8e0b722eaeb5596415f6aa65f39cef0e54b0a3","tid":278158,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T01:57:12.000Z","msg":"個app有乜用？"},{"pid":"168cbfdf6e35e281e68a4e0d442fe9fb55a29412","tid":278158,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-28T02:04:00